text: The material relating to the Statistics Division Records Control Schedule previously contained in 1.15.25 was incorporated into the November 2017 revision of Document 12990, Records and Information Management Records Control Schedules.
IRM 1.15.25 dated January 1, 2006 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
Director, Identity and Records Protection (IRP) Privacy, Governmental Liaison and Disclosure (PGLD)
